data.description: Welcome Home! This Move-In-Ready 3-bedroom 2.5 bath home is located in the desirable Ormond Lakes Community with a split floor plan with separate living areas and bonus room for a home office (2234 LV SQ FT)! Recent upgrades include a new roof in 2021, two TANKLESS hot water heaters installed in 2022, and fresh interior and exterior paint in 2023. Enter a spacious and naturally well-lit formal living and dining area. An additional bonus room adjacent to the living room provides the perfect space for an office or den, with convenient access to the backyard and large windows overlooking the rear yard. The generously sized kitchen is complete with a coffee bar, a center island cooktop, a spacious pantry, ample storage, and an adjoining laundry room that doubles as a butler's pantry! The kitchen seamlessly flows into a cozy breakfast nook and family room, creating an inviting ambiance. Large sliders open onto a spacious outdoor patio, perfect for dining and entertaining. Two  guest rooms share a bathroom, while a separate half bath is located just off the living room.  The private primary suite has a walk-in closet and sliders that lead to the bonus room. The ensuite bath features a large double vanity, a soothing soaking tub, and a walk-in shower. The Ormond Lakes Community offers a plethora of amenities, such as several miles of walking and biking sidewalks, a clubhouse, tennis courts, a fishing pier, a community pool, and convenient access to I-95. It is also conveniently located just a few minutes away from Tomoka State Park and the beautiful beach. Please note that square footage is based on tax records. Your dream home awaits - schedule a viewing today!
